data.help_classes

Class Request

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.help_classes.Request

  • public class Request
extends Object
    Entity class of a request (not an HTTP request). Holds all nessescary information of an request.

        The constructor checks if the arguments is legal. If they are not, IllegalArgumentException is thrown.
        Parameters:
        id - unique integer value for each request.
        sent - local date time of the time where offer was sent.
        comments - a string that describes the request (personalized by the employee).
        carport - a carport object.
        customer - a customer object.
        hasReceivedOffer - boolean if the offer has been recieved.
